tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE events (
    event_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    event_name STRING,
    event_date DATE,
    event_time TIME,
    event_location STRING,
    event_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE appointments (
    appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    event_id INT,
    participant_name VARCHAR(255),
    appointment_date DATE,
    appointment_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE appointments (
    appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    event_id INT,
    calendar_id INT,
    appointment_date DATE,
    appointment_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE Appointments (
    appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    appointment_date DATE,
    appointment_time TIME,
    event_id INT,
    calendar_id INT
);
